type: software
title: "A Hand For A Game: Real-time Hand Gesture Recognition for Gaming Applications"
abstract: >-
  An experimental computer vision system that enables real-time hand gesture 
  recognition for gaming applications. The system utilizes MediaPipe for hand 
  landmark detection and implements custom gesture interpretation algorithms 
  optimized for Windows gaming environments. This is a personal research 
  project with author-specific calibrations and is not intended for general 
  accessibility use or production deployment.

